title: Club disappeared
body: I am the owner of the club 7taus. However, it disappeared, my other club mates still has it with the tag. Idk what happened.

replies.body: Your club may be out of sync with your account and not showing up.  I tried to locate your club, but wasn't able to find it.  Toss me the correct club name as well as the tag, and I'll take a look into this for you personally.  Let me know!
